{"meta":{"title":"林博盛のBlog","subtitle":"","description":"","author":"LBSqc9","url":"http://LBSqc9.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"关于博主","date":"2024-05-08T10:26:41.891Z","updated":"2024-05-08T10:26:41.891Z","comments":true,"path":"about.html","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/about.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"文章归档","date":"2024-05-08T08:29:16.396Z","updated":"2024-05-08T08:29:16.396Z","comments":true,"path":"archives.html","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/archives.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"我的朋友","date":"2024-05-11T11:10:24.971Z","updated":"2024-05-11T11:10:24.971Z","comments":true,"path":"friend.html","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/friend.html","excerpt":"","text":"我的朋友"},{"title":"下载中心","date":"2024-05-08T08:13:30.663Z","updated":"2024-05-08T08:13:30.663Z","comments":true,"path":"download.html","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/download.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"对nexmoe主题做出的改动","slug":"对nexmoe主题做出的改动","date":"2024-05-09T07:07:36.000Z","updated":"2024-05-09T08:39:40.551Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/05/09/对nexmoe主题做出的改动/","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/2024/05/09/%E5%AF%B9nexmoe%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8/","excerpt":"","text":"将网页搜索引擎改为本地搜索写在前面后文中提到的主题文件夹的位置会因为安装该主题的方式不同出现差异，不同的安装方式下主题文件夹位置分别如下： 通过npm命令安装：node_modules/hexo-theme-nexmoe 通过解压主题安装：themes/nexmoe-x.x.x 更改搜索类型将主题配置文件中search项下的type设置为local，下面的url和id可以删除，改后如下： search: type: local 取消搜索区分大小写在搜索时将搜索关键词和文章标题、内容都转换为统一的大小写形式（比如全部转换为小写），然后进行匹配。这样无论用户输入的是大写、小写还是混合大小写，都能够正确匹配到相应的结果。 更改方式如下： 找到主题文件夹中的source/js/search.js 在keyword.forEach(word =&gt; &#123;下面添加const lowerCaseWord = word.toLowerCase(); 将const reg = new RegExp(lowerCaseWord, &#39;g&#39;);中的&#39;g&#39;改为&#39;gi&#39; 将if (post.title.search(reg) !== -1) &#123;改为if (post.title.toLowerCase().search(reg) !== -1) &#123; 将const textpos = post.text.search(reg);改为const textpos = post.text.toLowerCase().search(reg);","categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/categories/hexo/"}],"tags":[{"name":"主题优化","slug":"主题优化","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/categories/hexo/"}],"tags":[{"name":"主题优化","slug":"主题优化","permalink":"http://lbsqc9.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/"}]}